     H            Y.                                                      FEAR03
      ** RATR01 ***********************************
      * UPDATE OF IAF RATE FILE                   *                         *
      *   DISPLAY-ID  :    RATPW01                *
      *   CREATE DATE :    JUL/02/1997.           *
      *   AUTHOR      :    S.OHTAKE.              *
      *********************************************
     FRATPW01 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FRATPL01 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     E                    ER      1  10 60               ERORR MESSAGE
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        1   20WJI
     I                                        3   40WFN
      *
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           TEYY
     C                     KFLD           TEMM
     C                     KFLD           CODE
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PUSER  10
      *
     C                     MOVE PUSER     WUSER  10
      *
     C           STP0      TAG
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    KBN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    CODE
     C                     Z-ADD0         TEYY
     C                     Z-ADD0         TEMM
      ******************************************************
      *  DISPLAY  1 SCREEN                                 *
      ******************************************************
     C           STP1      TAG
     C                     EXFMTRATPW011
     C                     SETOF                     010203
     C                     SETOF                     5099
      *
     C           *INKA     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           KBN       IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     0199
     C                     MOVELER,1      MSG    60
     C                     GOTO STP1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           KBN       IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     50
     C                     MOVE 'DELETE'  KBNNM
     C                     GOTO ESC
     C                     ENDIF
     C           KBN       IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE 'CHANGE'  KBNNM
     C                     GOTO ESC
     C                     ENDIF
     C           KBN       IFEQ '2'
     C                     MOVE 'ADD   '  KBNNM
     C                     GOTO ESC
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     SETON                     0199
     C                     MOVELER,2      MSG    60
     C                     GOTO STP1
     C           ESC       TAG
      *
     C           CODE      IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     MOVELER,3      MSG    60
     C                     GOTO STP1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           TEYY      IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     0399
     C                     MOVELER,4      MSG    60
     C                     GOTO STP1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           TEMM      IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     0399
     C                     MOVELER,5      MSG    60
     C                     GOTO STP1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           TEMM      IFLT 1
     C           TEMM      IFGT 12
     C                     SETON                     0399
     C                     MOVELER,6      MSG    60
     C                     GOTO STP1
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    FLG     1
     C           KBN       IFEQ '0'
     C           KBN       OREQ '1'
     C                     SETOF                     80
     C           KEY1      CHAINRATPL011             80
     C           *IN80     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     MOVELER,8      MSG
     C                     GOTO STP1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           *IN80     IFEQ '0'
     C           RASKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           RASKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     MOVELER,9      MSG
     C                     GOTO STP1
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     Z-ADDRARATE    RATE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           KBN       IFEQ '2'
     C                     SETOF                     80
     C           KEY1      CHAINRATPL011             80
     C           *IN80     IFEQ '1'
     C                     Z-ADD0         RATE
     C                     GOTO JP
     C                     ENDIF
     C           *IN80     IFEQ '0'
     C           RASKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           RASKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     Z-ADD0         RATE
     C                     MOVE '*'       FLG
     C                     GOTO JP
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C           *IN80     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     MOVELER,7      MSG
     C                     GOTO STP1
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           JP        TAG
      ******************************************************
      *  DISPLAY  2 SCREEN                                 *
      ******************************************************
     C           STP2      TAG
     C                     EXFMTRATPW012
     C                     SETOF                     1099
      *
     C           *INKC     IFEQ '1'
     C                     GOTO STP0
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           KBN       IFEQ '0'
     C                     GOTO STP3
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           RATE      IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     1099
     C                     MOVELER,10     MSG
     C                     GOTO STP2
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           STP3      TAG
     C           *INKE     IFEQ '0'
     C                     GOTO STP2
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     MOVELWUSER     RAKOME
     C                     MOVE CODE      RACODE
     C                     Z-ADDTEYY      RATEYY
     C                     Z-ADDTEMM      RATEMM
     C                     Z-ADDRATE      RARATE
      *
     C           KBN       IFEQ '2'
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    RASKYY
     C                     Z-ADD0         RASKYY
     C                     Z-ADD0         RASKMM
     C                     Z-ADD0         RASKDD
     C                     Z-ADD*YEAR     RAKOYY
     C                     Z-ADD*MONTH    RAKOMM
     C                     Z-ADD*DAY      RAKODD
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C           FLG       IFEQ '*'
     C                     UPDATRATPL011
     C                     ELSE
     C                     WRITERATPL011
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           KBN       IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    RASKJY
     C                     Z-ADD0         RASKYY
     C                     Z-ADD0         RASKMM
     C                     Z-ADD0         RASKDD
     C                     Z-ADD*YEAR     RAKOYY
     C                     Z-ADD*MONTH    RAKOMM
     C                     Z-ADD*DAY      RAKODD
     C                     UPDATRATPL011
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           KBN       IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVE 'D'       RASKJY
     C                     Z-ADD*YEAR     RASKYY
     C                     Z-ADD*MONTH    RASKMM
     C                     Z-ADD*DAY      RASKDD
     C                     Z-ADD*YEAR     RAKOYY
     C                     Z-ADD*MONTH    RAKOMM
     C                     Z-ADD*DAY      RAKODD
     C                     UPDATRATPL011
     C                     ENDIF
** ERROR CODE
UPDATE ISN'T INPUT. INPUT IT.
UPDATE INSTRUCTION IS < 0 1 2>
CURRENCY CODE ISN'T INPUT. INPUT IT.
RANGE DATE(YEAR) ISN'T INPUT. INPUT IT.
RANGE DATE(MONTH) ISN'T INPUT. INPUT IT.
RANGE DATE(MONTH) ISN'T RIGHT.
IT INPUT ALREADY.
IT'S CANCELLED ALREADY.
THIS DATA IS DELETED.
CURRENCY RATE ISN'T INPUT. INPUT IT.
